      "author": "aaronpenne",
      "description": "Three new features:\n\n- **Skip subtasks with open parent**: don't move a completed subtask if its parent task is still open (off by default)\n- **Section-aware collection**: when collecting completed tasks, group them under sub-headings that mirror the original document structure (off by default)\n- **Per-note opt-out**: add `move-completed: false` to frontmatter to disable all auto-move and commands for that note\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/aaronpenne/move-completed-tasks/compare/0.3.2...0.4.0",
